OL,3,CSouth Tyneside Council 'frustrated'
OL,4,Cover waste collection backlog
OL,6,FSouth Tyneside Council says it is
OL,7,F'frustrated and disappointed' at an
OL,8,Fongoing backlog of bin collections in
OL,9,Fthe borough - saying it has concerns
OL,10,Fabout how much staff are following an
OL,11,Fagreed action plan.
OL,13,FThe local authority struck a deal with
OL,14,Fthe GMB union that the workforce would
OL,15,Fresume 'normal and established working
OL,16,Fpractices' from 7 May, but says
OL,17,Fworkers are currently completing
OL,18,Faround 55% of their weekly rounds.
