OL,3,CSouth Tyneside Council 'frustrated'
OL,4,Cover waste collection backlog
OL,6,FThe council says it is working hard to
OL,7,Favoid a build-up of waste as a result
OL,8,Fof the delays which have included some
OL,9,Frounds being missed completely.
OL,11,FMeanwhile, the GMB Union has said they
OL,12,Fare "shocked and surprised" by the
OL,13,Fcouncil's statement, affirming "no
OL,14,Findustrial action of any kind has
OL,15,Ftaken place for weeks."
OL,17,FAs a result, skips are being
OL,18,Freinstated from Saturday 1 June to
OL,19,FMonday 3 June inclusive at locations
OL,20,Facross South Tyneside to help clear
OL,21,Fthe backlog.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
