OL,3,CSouth Tyneside Council 'frustrated'
OL,4,Cover waste collection backlog
OL,6,FThe council added that it has
OL,7,Fcontacted the GMB union to state its
OL,8,Fconcerns.
OL,10,FStuart Wright, Director of Place and
OL,11,FCommunities for South Tyneside
OL,12,FCouncil, said: "Currently, crews are
OL,13,Fonly completing around 55 per cent of
OL,14,Ftheir weekly rounds, meaning they are
OL,15,Falmost a week behind because they are
OL,16,Fnot working as normal, despite a
OL,17,Fcommitment to do so and in direct
OL,18,Fcontravention of the MOU.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
