OL,3,CSouth Tyneside Council 'frustrated'
OL,4,Cover waste collection backlog
OL,6,F"We have asked the GMB to be clear
OL,7,Fwith their members precisely what is
OL,8,Fexpected of them. We appreciate that
OL,9,Fso much of our dialogue and
OL,10,Fnegotiations have been via the GMB and
OL,11,Fnot with the workforce direct, but
OL,12,Funfortunately, we have had no response
OL,13,Ffrom the GMB.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
