OL,3,CSouth Tyneside Council 'frustrated'
OL,4,Cover waste collection backlog
OL,6,F"We're also concerned that progress is
OL,7,Fbeing hampered by the refusal of some
OL,8,Funion members to participate in
OL,9,Fongoing dialogue. The degree to which
OL,10,Fprogress can be made in areas such as
OL,11,Fre-balancing bin rounds is limited if
OL,12,Funion members refuse to participate in
OL,13,Fthe necessary dialogue, as it is
OL,14,Fessential that we hear from the staff
OL,15,Fand work with them to make the
OL,16,Fimprovements they require.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
