OL,3,CSouth Tyneside Council 'frustrated'
OL,4,Cover waste collection backlog
OL,6,F"Our waste operatives are valued
OL,7,Femployees, and the action plan aims to
OL,8,Fbetter support them in their roles. It
OL,9,Fis vital that all parties engage in
OL,10,Fthe process so that we can work
OL,11,Fconstructively to deliver the plan and
OL,12,Fresume a full service for our
OL,13,Fresidents."
OL,15,FIn response to South Tyneside Councils
OL,16,Fstatement, the GMB union has blamed
OL,17,Fthe lack of bin collections on the
OL,18,Flocal authority's own "mismanagement".
