OL,3,CSouth Tyneside Council 'frustrated'
OL,4,Cover waste collection backlog
OL,6,FIn a statement, the GMB Union said:
OL,7,F"We are shocked and surprised by South
OL,8,FTyneside Councils decision to publicly
OL,9,Fissue a statement denouncing the
OL,10,Fworkforce for ongoing waste collection
OL,11,Fproblems across the county.
OL,13,F"Whilst there is an ongoing dispute
OL,14,Fover bullying and harassment in the
OL,15,Fservice GMB pause planned strike
OL,16,Faction following discussions with the
OL,17,Fauthority. No industrial action of any
OL,18,Fkind has taken place for weeks.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
