OL,3,CSouth Tyneside Council 'frustrated'
OL,4,Cover waste collection backlog
OL,6,F"Any ongoing collection issues are
OL,7,Fdown to the mismanagement of the
OL,8,Fservice, mismanagement that the GMB
OL,9,Fhave been highlighting for over a year.
OL,11,F"South Tyneside have had over eight
OL,12,Fweeks to organise the return to normal
OL,13,Fworking. It is a demonstration of the
OL,14,Fpoor management and leadership of the
OL,15,Fservice that they have both failed to
OL,16,Fget the service on track whilst also
OL,17,Fputting out misleading statements."
